{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-resources-article-template-js","path":"/resources/library/its-hard-to-keep-a-bad-market-down/","result":{"data":{"contentfulLibrary":{"title":"It’s Hard to Keep a Bad Market Down","youtube":null,"tags":["FINANCIAL MARKETS","RICH INSIGHTS"],"author":{"name":"Don Rich"},"description":{"description":"fiscal and monetary policy\nequity\nliquidity\nIMF\nearnings\nLEIs \nIndicators "},"childContentfulLibraryArticleRichTextNode":{"json":{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The flood of fiscal and monetary liquidity has driven equity prices up to all-time highs. This liquidity has resulted in prices becoming detached from economic reality, according to the IMF.  ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Is the recession over? Not hardly says the IMF.","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The chart below shows the IMF continues to downgrade its estimate of global growth this year.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The IMF is predicting a global recession this year that is magnitudes worse than anything we have experienced in the last 40 years. See below.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Is it any wonder why the IMF cautioned (in the text below chart) about the disconnect between market sentiment and economic reality. You think this slowdown might eventually show up in earnings?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The below chart comes from a Bloomberg article by Eric Martin.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"ibuw5oxk16h9","contentful_id":"ibuw5oxk16h9"}},"id":"c3tfExBfwKnvqE7jrl692aH","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-24T18:53:21.200Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-24T18:53:21.200Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment","contentful_id":"master"}},"revision":1,"contentful_id":"3tfExBfwKnvqE7jrl692aH"},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"Global Recession Deepens"},"description":{"en-US":"Global Recession Deepens"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/3tfExBfwKnvqE7jrl692aH/680d8e1818434f1092c2f4b212e772ed/Global_Recession_Deepens.png","details":{"size":158354,"image":{"width":866,"height":662}},"fileName":"Global Recession Deepens.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The IMF significantly downgraded their global growth projections based on their leading indicators. In our second chart, we review the leading economic indicators (LEIs) from the OECD.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"ibuw5oxk16h9","contentful_id":"ibuw5oxk16h9"}},"id":"c647C3mwWwcxHcLIAYOOV4z","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-24T18:56:36.466Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-24T18:56:36.466Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment","contentful_id":"master"}},"revision":1,"contentful_id":"647C3mwWwcxHcLIAYOOV4z"},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"Economic Cycle Indicator-U.S.& Global"},"description":{"en-US":"Economic Cycle Indicator-U.S.& Global"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/647C3mwWwcxHcLIAYOOV4z/630e4be19aef37c668b55b422a5cde89/Economic_Cycle_Indicator-U.S.__Globalpng.png","details":{"size":151891,"image":{"width":934,"height":638}},"fileName":"Economic Cycle Indicator-U.S.& Globalpng.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"This chart shows that the outlook has improved from April to May,","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":" but remains in very concerning territory","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":". Remember, the LEIs are supposed to reflect the outlook for the next 6-9 months. LEIs above 100 indicate economic expansion. ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":"We are clearly in contraction territory right now.","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]}},"publishDate":"June 24th, 2020","heroImage":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.998661311914324,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/dozjtqtmWksOFkbsCk6Km/67b9f61b6bc6b8fc551c7c28f03d6022/esoterica_blog-images_2x1__85_of_100_.jpg?w=1440&q=50&bg=rgb%3A000000","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/dozjtqtmWksOFkbsCk6Km/67b9f61b6bc6b8fc551c7c28f03d6022/esoterica_blog-images_2x1__85_of_100_.jpg?w=360&h=180&q=50&bg=rgb%3A000000 360w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/dozjtqtmWksOFkbsCk6Km/67b9f61b6bc6b8fc551c7c28f03d6022/esoterica_blog-images_2x1__85_of_100_.jpg?w=720&h=360&q=50&bg=rgb%3A000000 720w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/dozjtqtmWksOFkbsCk6Km/67b9f61b6bc6b8fc551c7c28f03d6022/esoterica_blog-images_2x1__85_of_100_.jpg?w=1440&h=720&q=50&bg=rgb%3A000000 1440w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ibuw5oxk16h9/dozjtqtmWksOFkbsCk6Km/67b9f61b6bc6b8fc551c7c28f03d6022/esoterica_blog-images_2x1__85_of_100_.jpg?w=1493&h=747&q=50&bg=rgb%3A000000 1493w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}},"contentfulGlossary":null},"pageContext":{"slug":"its-hard-to-keep-a-bad-market-down","postType":"library"}},"staticQueryHashes":["219754891","2939829994","70770681"]}